## Description {#details}

Utility to find all debug info in a module.

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/debuginfofinder">DebugInfoFinder</a> tries to list all debug info MDNodes used in a module. To list debug info MDNodes used by an instruction, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/debuginfofinder">DebugInfoFinder</a> uses processDeclare, processValue and processLocation to handle <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbgdeclareinst">DbgDeclareInst</a>, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/dbgvalueinst">DbgValueInst</a> and DbgLoc attached to instructions. processModule will go through all DICompileUnits in llvm.dbg.cu and list debug info MDNodes used by the CUs.

Definition at line 105 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/ir/debuginfo-h">DebugInfo.h</a>.
